itting on a huge gain of 28.6% this year, the average year-to-date change for these country</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743176-argentina-etf-on-top-in-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 09:00:00"}, {"id": "4743163", "title": "BHK: 4 Reasons Why I Am Cautious", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"forex charts\" data-id=\"165999267\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5184px\" height=\"3456px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Adam Smigielski</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The BlackRock Core Bond Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYS