 hate groups and political violence.</li> </ul> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regardless of which side of the political divide you find yourself, please be courteous and don't direct abuse at other users.</p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">For any issue with regards to comments please email us at : moderation@seekingalpha.com.</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>Seeking Alpha's Disclosure:</span></b><span> Past performance is no guarantee of future results. No recommendation or advice is being given as to whether any investment is suitable for a particular investor. Any views or opinions expressed above may not reflect those of Seeking Alpha as a whole. Seeking Alpha is not a licensed securities dealer, broker or US investment adviser or investment bank. Our analysts are third party authors that include both professional investors and individual investors who may not be licensed or certified by any institute or regulatory body.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"> </p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <div class=\"sa-art article-width paywall-full-content\" id=\"a-body\"><span class=\"content-end p p1\"></span></div>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740940-politics-and-the-markets-121024", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 08:00:00"}, {"id": "4743155", "title": "Masco Corporation: Still Not Cheap Enough, Especially Given Mixed Results", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Coloured liquid splash\" data-id=\"829578556\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1286px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Henrik Sorensen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Whenever I rate a company a \u2018hold,\u2019 it is a representation of my belief that shares are unlikely to perform materially different from the broader market will for the foreseeable future. One good example of this that I could point</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/829578556/image_829578556.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743155-masco-corporation-still-not-cheap-enough-mixed-results", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 07:55:08"}, {"id": "4743164", "title": "November Jobs Report: Not Enough To Alter The Fed's Course", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business Planning\" data-id=\"175599141\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">blackred</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Originally published on December 6, 2024</em></p> <p><em>By Christian Floro, CFA, CMT, Market Strategist</em></p> <p>The November jobs report showed a 227,000 gain in jobs, rebounding from last month\u2019s weather and strike-induced weakness. Despite the bounce back, with surprisingly limited revisions over the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743164-november-jobs-report-not-enough-to-alter-the-fed-course", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 07:50:00"}, {"id": "4743160", "title": "Don't Underestimate Inflation's Knack For Dampening Retirement Spirits", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Overhead view of young Asian women managing home finance using smartphone. She is working with household utility bill and calculating expenses at home.\" data-id=\"1811771950\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Images By Tang Ming Tung</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Inflation may have cooled from its recent multi-decade highs, but for retirees and those nearing retirement, the battle against rising costs is far from over. Age-related price pressures, particularly in healthcare and other essentials, tend to accelerate just as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1811771950/image_1811771950.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743160-dont-underestimate-inflation-knack-for-dampening-retirement-spirits", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 07:35:00"}, {"id": "4743154", "title": "AvePoint Keeps Getting Better", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Clouds in server room\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1287px\" data-id=\"470621083\" data-type=\"getty-image\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Colin Anderson Productions pty ltd</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4722681-avepoint-a-solid-saas-data-management-play-benefiting-from-the-ai-revolution\">recommended</a> the shares of AvePoint (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVPT\" title=\"AvePoint, Inc.\">AVPT</a></span>) in September and 